<en-note><div><span style="font-weight: bold;">How to setup the Static IP</span><br/></div><div>Edit  &quot;<span style="font-style: italic;">/etc/rc.conf</span>&quot;</div><div>ifconfig_xn0=&quot;inet 10.10.10.150 netmask 255.255.255.0&quot;</div><div>         defaultrouter=&quot;10.10.10.10&quot;</div><div>Edit &quot;/etc/resolv.conf&quot;</div><div>nameserver 192.168.21</div><div>        nameserver 10.10.10.120</div><div><br/></div><div>How to &quot;Start&quot;,&quot;Stop&quot; or &quot;Restart&quot;  interfaces:</div><div>=&gt; sudo /etc/rc.d/netif start | stop | restart</div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold;">To see the list of &quot;Up/Down&quot; interfaces:</span></div><div>=&gt; ifconfig -u  | -d</div><div><br/></div><div><span style="font-weight: bold;">To update the &quot;Routing&quot; table:</span></div><div>=&gt; /etc/rc.d/routing restart</div><div><br/></div><div>Note: Over SSH you must use &quot;&amp;&amp;&quot; to avoid disconnection:</div><div>=&gt; sudo /etc/rc.d/netif restart &amp;&amp; sudo </div><div><br/></div></en-note>
